==English==
===Adjective===
'''Reckless'''

#A person having performed an action or method which is unwise, or does not take account of the risks (to yourself or others).  Conjugated with ''To be'', otherwise '''Reckless-ly'''.  "He is reckless.", "I was reckless".

===Noun===
'''Recklessness'''
# - The quality of being reckless.